moonslime.Archaeology.glass_path.name: Glass Path
moonslime.Archaeology.glass_path.descrip: Place on the ground to create paths or to spruce up your floors.

moonslime.Archaeology.bone_path.descript: Place on the ground to create paths or to make your floors terrifying.
moonslime.Archaeology.rust_path.name: Rusty Path
moonslime.Archaeology.rust_path.descript: Place on the ground to create paths or to make your floors rustic.
moonslime.Archaeology.totem_volcano_warp: A device made from your studies of artifacts. Warps you to version of the Volcano that you can climb infinitely. Warning: Bring a warping item to escape.
moonslime.Archaeology.diggers_delight.de: A nice cold tasty treat to have before you start digging in the dirt!
moonslime.Archaeology.rocky_root.name: Rocky Root Coffee
moonslime.Archaeology.rocky_root.descrip: WARNING: Do not actually drink the stone. it's there for flavor.

moonslime.Archaeology.ancient_battery.de: Using knowledge gained from studing artifacts, you can make battery packs the old fashion way! Use juice, clay, and time to make them at this station.
moonslime.Archaeology.preservation_chamb: 在这里陈列工艺品和古物
